Key Takeaways
Management Groups help organize and govern Azure subscriptions.
RBAC supports both built-in and custom roles.
Assigning roles to groups is a best practice.
Azure custom roles are created using JSON.
RBAC inheritance simplifies permission management.
Activity Logs provide auditing and monitoring capabilities.
Proper cleanup is an important operational practice.
